reviewText: Only one of the three disks actually played. Tried several different DVD players but only one title would load and play. VERY disappointing!
An FZ Kinder Egg! 3-in-1 of great entertainment!

I waited on line, freezing cold December in NYC on opening night to see the first public show. I have waited almost 35 years to own my very own copy. It really captures FZ's Halloween shows. Awesome musicians and claymation.
